description:
You can no longer tell what's real online. Voice cloning scams, political deepfakes, AI generated tragedies, synthetic influencers, the internet is drowning in AI content that's increasingly impossible to detect.

#AIslop

00:00 Intro
00:52 Marco Rubio Impersonation
01:51 AI Generated Tragedies

08:46 Etsy AI Scams
10:07 AI Crystal Mug Scam
12:23 AI Generated ASMR
